Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:05.060
Now let's explore the project section,
this is optional but highly recommended.

00:00:05.060 --> 00:00:08.220
It can be an especially helpful way to
demonstrate your practical experience.

00:00:09.270 --> 00:00:10.250
When creating content for

00:00:10.250 --> 00:00:13.940
your project section, there are a few
guidelines to keep in mind.

00:00:13.940 --> 00:00:18.080
Include the project title as well as
a concise description about the project.

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:21.180
Use keywords and
note any coding languages you applied,

00:00:21.180 --> 00:00:23.580
the most recent projects
would be at the top.

00:00:23.580 --> 00:00:26.470
Finally, keep in mind that you
can adjust the placement of your

00:00:26.470 --> 00:00:28.870
projects in your overall
LinkedIn profile.

00:00:28.870 --> 00:00:31.850
If you are trying to switch careers
entirely, placing your projects

00:00:31.850 --> 00:00:34.870
above your work experience may better
reflect your goals to recruiters.

